\f0\b\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf2 \cb3 Overview and Preamble
\f1\b0 \'a0
\f2\fs24 \cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa213\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf2 \cb3 Trading conditions\'a0remain\'a0challenging\'a0this year due to poor weather and tough economics. The original March plan (Your Classics, UGC-focused campaign) relies too heavily on community input and\'a0doesn't\'a0drive enough commercial results. We need to pivot to a commercially focused campaign without resorting to\'a0over indexing\'a0SALE messaging.\'a0\'a0
\f2\fs24 \cb1 \

\f1\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cb3 The Bike That Gets You\cf5 \cb3 \ul \ulc5 \strokec5 \'94\cf2 \cb3 \ulnone \strokec2 \'a0celebrates\'a0built to order\'a0approach. Our bikes are designed, engineered and precision-built in the North of England. Proper bikes for proper riding\'a0- the right bike\'a0isn't\'a0a generic compromise;\'a0it's\'a0built for you. This March,\'a0we're\'a0helping riders across all categories find their perfect build before the season starts.\'a0
\f2\fs24 \cb1 \

\f1\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cb3 This messaging is supported by commercial action across road, gravel,\'a0CGR,\'a0Sportfit\'a0and e-bike ranges. Aligned with\'a0February weekend and\'a0natural spring motivation and the moment riders commit to their season.\'a0
\f2\fs24 \cb1 \

\f1\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cb3 Starting in week one with an overview of\'a0bikes within each category and followed up each week, with a deep dive for each category\'a0and a bike of the week.\'a0\'a0
\f2\fs24 \cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa213\partightenfactor0

