\f0\b\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cb3 Bullseye
\f1\b0 :\'a0\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb3 Male and female riders aged 30-45 who are planning their cycling season. These are committed riders who take cycling seriously but\'a0aren't\'a0necessarily racing. They ride 2-4 times per week when in season. Mixed between road purists, gravel adventurers, and those who want both. Some are returning after winter;\'a0others are looking to upgrade before their big season goals. They have disposable income for quality equipment and value getting it right over getting it cheap.\'a0
