\f1\b0 \'a0
\f2\fs24 \cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa213\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf2 \cb3 March\'a0represents\'a0possibility. Longer days, better weather, and the promise of the riding season ahead.\'a0They're\'a0motivated by personal goals (first sportive, regular group rides, gravel events, fitness targets) rather than competition.\'a0They're\'a0looking for justification to upgrade. They respond to authenticity and hate being sold to. They value quality, performance, and getting it right over getting it cheap.\'a0
